node.text: Our newest instructor, a James Beard Award–winning executive chef and partner at The Grey, creates dishes that celebrate African American and  Southern cuisine. Now she’s teaching you traditional and reimagined recipes, plus techniques like braising, pickling, and smoking to add texture and flavor. Introducing @mashamabailey’s class on Southern cooking.

node.title: Mashama Bailey Teaches U.S. Southern Cooking
